<ArticleParagraph
  articlePText={`Schlesisches Tor — Kreuzberg - Beneath the U-Bahn tracks. This booth hums with the rhythm of Kreuzberg. The grainy strips feel cinematic, like stills pulled from a Berlin indie film.`}
/>
<ArticleParagraph
  articlePText={`RAW 2 — Revaler Str. 99, 10245 Berlin. Set against graffiti walls and industrial textures, this booth spits out high-contrast photos that echo the grit of its surroundings.`}
